# ðŸŽ® Guess the Word - Python Console Game

A simple word guessing game written in Python.  
The player has **10 attempts** to guess the hidden word by entering letters one by one.  

The system randomly selects a word from a predefined word pool, and your goal is to guess it letter by letter.  
At each step, the game gives you feedback on your progress.  

